<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WebXR Platformer Game</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0f172a;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
            --primary: #8b5cf6;
            --primary-hover: #7c3aed;
            --text: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
        }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #a78bfa, #e879f9);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .badges {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .badges img {
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #e2e8f0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--card-bg);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #334155;
        }
        .card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #a78bfa;
        }
        ul.features {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        ul.features li {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
        }
        code {
            background: #0f172a;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: #38bdf8;
            font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        .play-btn {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 0 auto 60px;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
        }
        .play-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>🎮 WebXR Platformer</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">An immersive 3D Virtual Reality platformer built with React, Three.js, and WebXR.</p>
        
        <div class="badges">
            <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/React-20232A?style=for-the-badge&logo=react&logoColor=61DAFB" alt="React" />
            <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/ThreeJs-black?style=for-the-badge&logo=three.js&logoColor=white" alt="Three.js" />
            <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/WebXR-8A2BE2?style=for-the-badge&logo=virtual-reality&logoColor=white" alt="WebXR" />
        </div>

        <!-- Replace # with the actual link to your hosted game -->
        <a href="#" class="play-btn">Play the Game</a>

        <h2>🌟 Features</h2>
        <ul class="features">
            <li><strong>Full VR Support:</strong> Built with <code>@react-three/xr</code> for native WebXR experiences.</li>
            <li><strong>Physics Engine:</strong> Powered by <code>@react-three/rapier</code> for realistic gravity, collisions, and rigid bodies.</li>
            <li><strong>Interactive Mechanics:</strong> Moving platforms, fake floors, hidden spikes, and falling blocks.</li>
            <li><strong>Desktop Fallback:</strong> Playable in the browser without a headset using keyboard controls.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>🕹️ Controls</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>🥽 VR Headset</h3>
                <p><strong>Move:</strong> Left Controller Thumbstick</p>
                <p><strong>Jump:</strong> Right Controller Trigger or 'A' Button</p>
                <p><strong>Interact:</strong> Point and click with controllers on 3D UI buttons</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>⌨️ Desktop (Fallback)</h3>
                <p><strong>Move:</strong> <code>W</code> <code>A</code> <code>S</code> <code>D</code> or Arrow Keys</p>
                <p><strong>Jump:</strong> <code>Spacebar</code></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
